{"tid":2178112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實辯論要贏人係咪真係靠論點？","createTime":"2020-08-28T07:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T08:43:26.000Z","uid":128261,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"04d934e0380b4c49ce8d5dffda262edc285d2bd0","tid":2178112,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"有時同啲藍絲辯論，明明對方啲觀點好廢好荒謬<br />\n但辯辯下又好似慢慢比對方牽住鼻子走咁<br />\n不利既論點就快快spin走或者輕輕回應<br />\n有利既論點就不斷重覆，面對質疑都照講落去，係咁反問人<br />\n然後明明無證據又鐘意一口咬定啲野<br />\n呢啲詭辯技巧真係好強大<br />\n到底邊度有得學返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd15aebe026f8a4c8e15a937806639a56dc2edf","tid":2178112,"uid":231583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a128296e5333f45ae49e213d46618aa4d1bf720","tid":2178112,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fd15aebe026f8a4c8e15a937806639a56dc2edf","tid":2178112,"uid":231583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"類似係咁<br />\n於是我就會越來越勞氣，講野之前思考既時間少左<br />\n咁就會製造啲位比藍絲入<br />\n然後藍絲就會乘機捉住再不斷發酵"},{"pid":"325dc3e39470afd8189ece26d958ab0a23d1c89a","tid":2178112,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd2362e9a686b0600865f8ba6986142ef6a794c8","tid":2178112,"uid":59134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:32:02.000Z","msg":"藍絲係靠威迫利誘<br />\n中國人傳統就係死都唔肯認低威<br />\n而且佢地嘅所謂主見係隨波逐流<br />\n如果你改變到佢嘅圈子就可以改變佢嘅諗法"},{"pid":"be8d17169d17e17687d44ff11ccf670f6f46f612","tid":2178112,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"五毛經驗係豐富啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a2939d93d20c7094d0ee2d72aaea88b447d753","tid":2178112,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"325